1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:15,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,620 --> 00:01:39,970
[Moonlight]

3
00:01:40,140 --> 00:01:43,000
[Episode 12]

4
00:01:45,030 --> 00:01:47,100
Both of you are dating?

5
00:01:50,070 --> 00:01:51,190
So, what's going on?

6
00:01:52,750 --> 00:01:53,990
I dragged her into some trouble before,

7
00:01:53,990 --> 00:01:55,150
and caused her to lose out on her salary.

8
00:01:55,150 --> 00:01:56,430
She almost had to sleep on the street.

9
00:01:56,670 --> 00:01:57,539
That period

10
00:01:57,539 --> 00:01:59,270
was when Book of Luo He God

11
00:01:59,270 --> 00:02:00,710
was about to be prepared.

12
00:02:00,710 --> 00:02:02,670
I was afraid that her being homeless

13
00:02:02,670 --> 00:02:04,350
would affect her creativity,

14
00:02:04,350 --> 00:02:05,550
so I lent her my second-floor room.

15
00:02:06,790 --> 00:02:08,390
Why are you so nervous?

16
00:02:08,830 --> 00:02:11,470
So, why was she in your room?

17
00:02:11,860 --> 00:02:12,870
Was it to hide from me?

18
00:02:13,350 --> 00:02:14,110
Yes!

19
00:02:17,190 --> 00:02:18,550
So, the two of you really don't

20
00:02:18,550 --> 00:02:20,830
have that kind of relationship
that I imagined?

21
00:02:20,830 --> 00:02:22,230
No!

22
00:02:28,460 --> 00:02:29,750
It seems I still have a chance.

23
00:02:32,540 --> 00:02:33,350
That's good.

24
00:02:33,750 --> 00:02:34,990
What's so good?

25
00:02:36,230 --> 00:02:37,150
Chu Li.

26
00:02:38,790 --> 00:02:39,470
Hey!

27
00:02:43,540 --> 00:02:44,230
Don't make noise.

28
00:02:47,790 --> 00:02:48,380
Chu Li.

29
00:02:50,390 --> 00:02:51,510
I like you.

30
00:02:55,790 --> 00:02:56,860
But...

31
00:02:57,510 --> 00:02:58,750
Sir...

32
00:02:59,820 --> 00:03:01,260
What's your problem, Jiang Yu Cheng?

33
00:03:01,510 --> 00:03:02,390
You eat when you're tired,

34
00:03:02,390 --> 00:03:03,110
you sleep when you're hungry.

35
00:03:03,110 --> 00:03:03,990
If you're sick go see a doctor,

36
00:03:03,990 --> 00:03:04,790
don't be crazy here!

37
00:03:06,030 --> 00:03:06,790
Chu Li.

38
00:03:08,070 --> 00:03:09,150
I know this is very sudden,

39
00:03:09,590 --> 00:03:10,620
but I'm not joking.

40
00:03:15,750 --> 00:03:16,590
Zhou Chuan,

41
00:03:17,270 --> 00:03:19,230
Chu Li is our editor.

42
00:03:21,070 --> 00:03:22,500
She isn't one of your underlings,

43
00:03:22,500 --> 00:03:23,750
and definitely isn't your belonging.

44
00:03:23,750 --> 00:03:24,990
To you,

45
00:03:25,230 --> 00:03:27,340
she is nothing but your editor.

46
00:03:29,030 --> 00:03:30,910
To me...

47
00:03:30,910 --> 00:03:31,710
Yes.

48
00:03:32,590 --> 00:03:33,870
But to me,

49
00:03:35,470 --> 00:03:37,630
I hope that she becomes my girlfriend.

50
00:03:50,780 --> 00:03:51,750
It's okay.

51
00:03:52,590 --> 00:03:53,990
Don't rush to answer me.

52
00:03:55,270 --> 00:03:56,590
About Book of Luo He God,

53
00:03:56,590 --> 00:03:57,590
it was done very well.

54
00:03:58,070 --> 00:03:59,260
My publishing agreement

55
00:03:59,750 --> 00:04:00,870
can be signed tomorrow.

56
00:04:01,900 --> 00:04:02,870
Really?

57
00:04:02,870 --> 00:04:04,100
That's amazing!

58
00:04:04,100 --> 00:04:05,950
I'll meet you at 2 p.m. tomorrow.

59
00:04:05,950 --> 00:04:06,740
Okay!

60
00:04:08,430 --> 00:04:10,260
Leave now!

61
00:04:10,260 --> 00:04:12,270
Leave, what are you looking at? Leave!

62
00:04:13,030 --> 00:04:14,430
Leave!

63
00:04:17,430 --> 00:04:18,510
I'm warning you now.

64
00:04:18,990 --> 00:04:20,820
Don't be fooled by his sweet words.

65
00:04:21,790 --> 00:04:24,339
It's impossible between you two.

66
00:04:24,339 --> 00:04:25,350
I...

67
00:04:26,950 --> 00:04:28,310
Why is it impossible?

68
00:04:30,180 --> 00:04:32,310
So, you actually want to be with him?

69
00:04:34,430 --> 00:04:37,270
I have not slept since last night,

70
00:04:37,270 --> 00:04:39,150
so my head is really dizzy.

71
00:04:39,150 --> 00:04:40,790
I'm going to catch up on sleep.

72
00:04:47,990 --> 00:04:48,950
Sir,

73
00:04:49,270 --> 00:04:50,230
good night!

74
00:05:05,990 --> 00:05:06,910
Oh god,

75
00:05:06,910 --> 00:05:09,270
he can't be telling the truth, right?

76
00:05:12,030 --> 00:05:14,300
[Why is it not him?]

77
00:05:20,230 --> 00:05:23,390
What should I do?

78
00:05:24,710 --> 00:05:27,270
God, he's just too good.

79
00:05:31,030 --> 00:05:32,750
Why do you think it's him?

80
00:05:33,710 --> 00:05:35,150
What could she possibly mean?

81
00:05:36,230 --> 00:05:39,110
Could it be she really likes
Jiang Yu Cheng?

82
00:05:44,150 --> 00:05:45,350
Hey, is this Wu Ye?

83
00:05:45,659 --> 00:05:47,230
How do I change the house's password?

84
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:50,360
[Corner Bookstore]

85
00:05:51,350 --> 00:05:52,670
Mr Jiang, don't worry.

86
00:05:52,670 --> 00:05:54,550
I won't let you down.

87
00:05:59,670 --> 00:06:00,710
I know.

88
00:06:02,270 --> 00:06:04,909
Why are you speaking so softly?

89
00:06:06,510 --> 00:06:07,710
Do you believe it?

90
00:06:14,190 --> 00:06:16,670
[What are they talking about?]

91
00:06:16,670 --> 00:06:19,310
[These bookshelves block sound so well!]

92
00:06:19,870 --> 00:06:21,230
Zhou Chuan is in this bookstore

93
00:06:21,230 --> 00:06:22,630
looking at us from some corner.

94
00:06:23,230 --> 00:06:24,710
No way.

95
00:06:36,430 --> 00:06:37,710
Mr Zhou Chuan.

96
00:06:37,710 --> 00:06:40,430
Are you looking for a book? Need any help?

97
00:06:44,630 --> 00:06:46,270
You have sharp eyes.

98
00:06:46,270 --> 00:06:48,260
You can recognise me in this disguise.

99
00:06:49,070 --> 00:06:50,310
I...

100
00:06:51,710 --> 00:06:54,510
Nothing, I'm just browsing.

101
00:06:58,270 --> 00:06:59,470
I'm leaving.

102
00:07:16,830 --> 00:07:19,390
I hope I didn't scare you yesterday.

103
00:07:22,430 --> 00:07:24,350
Sorry, I didn't mean it.

104
00:07:24,350 --> 00:07:25,230
However,

105
00:07:25,230 --> 00:07:26,990
I meant everything I said yesterday.

106
00:07:26,990 --> 00:07:28,790
I hope you can consider it seriously.

107
00:07:30,910 --> 00:07:32,060
Mr Jiang,

108
00:07:32,430 --> 00:07:36,190
I'm honoured that you like me.

109
00:07:36,190 --> 00:07:37,460
However...

110
00:07:38,510 --> 00:07:41,670
Anyway, I'm sorry, Mr Jiang.

111
00:07:43,790 --> 00:07:44,909
It's okay.

112
00:07:45,190 --> 00:07:46,820
I won't give up just because

113
00:07:46,820 --> 00:07:48,190
you have feelings for someone else.

114
00:07:50,870 --> 00:07:52,540
You should just give up.

115
00:07:55,150 --> 00:07:56,150
I'm done signing.

116
00:07:56,150 --> 00:07:57,590
I'll send you back to
Yuan Yue Publishing House.

117
00:08:00,020 --> 00:08:01,070
Ms Liu, low down.

118
00:08:09,470 --> 00:08:11,710
Today's weather is really nice.

119
00:08:12,390 --> 00:08:13,430
Bai Zhi,

120
00:08:13,710 --> 00:08:15,870
let's take a walk in the yard.

121
00:08:15,870 --> 00:08:16,710
Of course.

122
00:08:16,950 --> 00:08:18,470
I'll take over. Thank you.

123
00:08:20,860 --> 00:08:27,790
♫ They say strange things
and keep rapport ♫

124
00:08:28,450 --> 00:08:35,520
♫ Guileless adults are reduced to a joke ♫

125
00:08:28,510 --> 00:08:30,710
Today's weather is really nice.

126
00:08:31,190 --> 00:08:33,390
I haven't felt such wind in a while.

127
00:08:35,110 --> 00:08:38,710
Back then when the old man was around,

128
00:08:35,970 --> 00:08:42,289
♫ Unceasingly, here to stay ♫

129
00:08:38,710 --> 00:08:42,030
he liked to hold my hands
and walk with me in the park.

130
00:08:43,140 --> 00:08:44,950
With a light breeze on our faces,

131
00:08:43,179 --> 00:08:49,520
♫ No dancing on the roof, but rain ♫

132
00:08:45,900 --> 00:08:48,630
seeing light peek through the trees,

133
00:08:49,590 --> 00:08:52,030
listening to birds and insects chirp.

134
00:08:50,900 --> 00:08:57,750
♫ The loneliness has found
a place and moved out ♫

135
00:08:53,310 --> 00:08:56,950
All the worries we had

136
00:08:57,340 --> 00:08:59,870
would fade away with the wind.

137
00:08:58,430 --> 00:09:05,380
♫ Guests sillier than me
argue and exaggerate ♫

138
00:09:00,950 --> 00:09:04,870
That was the happiest time of my life.

139
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:12,800
♫ The moon is
outrageously beautiful tonight ♫

140
00:09:08,830 --> 00:09:11,540
Ms Liu, I will come more often

141
00:09:11,540 --> 00:09:14,790
and spend more time walking with you.

142
00:09:12,890 --> 00:09:19,510
♫ Lend me the light on your face ♫

143
00:09:18,390 --> 00:09:19,830
I still remember

144
00:09:19,830 --> 00:09:23,910
when you and Jiang visited me at home.

145
00:09:19,970 --> 00:09:27,960
♫ I've been giddy from drifting
in a sea of people ♫

146
00:09:24,270 --> 00:09:26,310
He was holding your hand,

147
00:09:26,310 --> 00:09:29,070
and did not let go even
after both of you left.

148
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:35,160
♫ Unwilling to admit my anticipation
of getting submitted to gentleness ♫

149
00:09:29,580 --> 00:09:33,470
I could feel that both of you are happy.

150
00:09:35,190 --> 00:09:37,750
Ms Liu, those are all past.

151
00:09:35,570 --> 00:09:42,800
♫ I want to be led by you,
albeit a meager freedom ♫

152
00:09:38,750 --> 00:09:41,870
The experiences of two people together

153
00:09:41,870 --> 00:09:44,070
are what made up the past.

154
00:09:42,910 --> 00:09:47,090
♫ The Hand of the Creator
has finally seen to ♫

155
00:09:45,100 --> 00:09:48,740
It is only when we lose someone,

156
00:09:47,410 --> 00:09:53,950
♫ The alien's call for help ♫

157
00:09:49,150 --> 00:09:51,910
then we regret not treasuring

158
00:09:51,910 --> 00:09:53,750
whatever we used to have.

159
00:09:55,510 --> 00:09:57,670
When I was just married,

160
00:09:59,110 --> 00:10:00,390
I couldn't stand the snoring

161
00:10:00,390 --> 00:10:02,790
of my husband at all.

162
00:10:04,510 --> 00:10:06,830
It was so noisy every night

163
00:10:06,830 --> 00:10:09,270
and I couldn't sleep at all.

164
00:10:07,820 --> 00:10:14,260
♫ To always be a source of warmth
just for you ♫

165
00:10:11,790 --> 00:10:14,310
But as time passed,

166
00:10:14,310 --> 00:10:15,790
I got used to it.

167
00:10:15,390 --> 00:10:22,480
♫ A mysterious weakness, came into being ♫

168
00:10:18,660 --> 00:10:21,710
Now, he isn't here anymore.

169
00:10:22,070 --> 00:10:25,230
There's no snoring
and it's not noisy anymore.

170
00:10:22,790 --> 00:10:30,200
♫ Melting, chewing ♫

171
00:10:25,590 --> 00:10:27,900
But, I'm not longer used to it.

172
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:37,650
♫ There's no hiding at the dining table.
There's only our joined souls ♫

173
00:10:30,830 --> 00:10:32,790
We can't turn the time.

174
00:10:36,230 --> 00:10:37,470
You

175
00:10:38,070 --> 00:10:40,830
are just too headstrong.

176
00:10:40,640 --> 00:10:48,440
♫ I'm drifting in a sea of people.
And will frequently look back ♫

177
00:10:40,830 --> 00:10:43,980
You never willing to give in.

178
00:10:44,350 --> 00:10:48,150
That's why your relationship has trouble.

179
00:10:48,620 --> 00:10:56,300
♫ Scared to reach out my hand
that no one will save me ♫

180
00:10:49,510 --> 00:10:52,340
Ms Liu, I'm really fine now.

181
00:10:52,340 --> 00:10:53,630
No one is troubling me.

182
00:10:55,110 --> 00:10:57,030
It's because you lose someone

183
00:10:56,300 --> 00:11:03,510
♫ How rich can concrete skyscrapers be ♫

184
00:10:57,430 --> 00:10:58,710
that made your life

185
00:10:59,270 --> 00:11:01,950
less wonderful.

186
00:11:03,650 --> 00:11:07,490
♫ You are a rare shining oasis ♫

187
00:11:03,780 --> 00:11:04,750
Bai Zhi,

188
00:11:05,510 --> 00:11:07,790
you need to think this through.

189
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:20,800
♫ Exactly what I want ♫

190
00:11:38,190 --> 00:11:39,100
Chu Li,

191
00:11:39,100 --> 00:11:41,830
didn't you go get Mr Jiang's signature?

192
00:11:42,740 --> 00:11:44,150
Why did you buy something too?

193
00:11:44,150 --> 00:11:45,990
Mr Jiang bought these for all of you.

194
00:11:45,990 --> 00:11:47,550
He wants to extend
his regards to everyone.

195
00:11:48,990 --> 00:11:49,870
Chu Li,

196
00:11:50,150 --> 00:11:51,670
Mr Jiang has signed the contract, right?

197
00:11:57,430 --> 00:11:58,430
It doesn't matter if he lost popularity.

198
00:11:58,430 --> 00:11:59,870
This book will still sell well.

199
00:12:01,510 --> 00:12:02,750
To you, is the quality of an author

200
00:12:02,750 --> 00:12:05,390
only defined by his marketability?

201
00:12:05,390 --> 00:12:06,430
Since you like numbers so much,

202
00:12:06,430 --> 00:12:08,430
circulation department
is more suitable for you.

203
00:12:16,630 --> 00:12:19,230
Chu Li, what colour do you like?

204
00:12:19,630 --> 00:12:21,510
Take whichever flavour you like.

205
00:12:21,830 --> 00:12:22,750
Thank you.

206
00:12:25,470 --> 00:12:35,630
[Flying Elephant: Teatime welfare
provided by Mr Jiang]

207
00:12:31,110 --> 00:12:33,460
Teatime welfare.

208
00:12:33,460 --> 00:12:35,630
Greetings from Mr Jiang?

209
00:12:37,190 --> 00:12:39,270
That Jiang is really crafty.

210
00:12:39,270 --> 00:12:40,990
He even sent welfare to the editors.

211
00:12:42,310 --> 00:12:44,270
These underhanded tactics...

212
00:12:52,630 --> 00:12:53,380
Hello?

213
00:12:53,380 --> 00:12:55,310
Stay away from those macarons.

214
00:12:55,550 --> 00:12:56,990
[You'll become fat.]

215
00:12:57,830 --> 00:12:59,230
How do you know about it?

216
00:12:59,230 --> 00:13:00,470
You don't have to know.

217
00:13:00,470 --> 00:13:01,350
You are not allowed to eat the desserts.

218
00:13:02,190 --> 00:13:04,550
Sir, you sounded like

219
00:13:04,550 --> 00:13:06,310
the desserts are laced with arsenic.

220
00:13:06,310 --> 00:13:07,550
Why can't I eat it?

221
00:13:07,550 --> 00:13:08,390
I...

222
00:13:10,790 --> 00:13:13,110
This is a kind reminder from me.

223
00:13:13,430 --> 00:13:14,590
Your body weight

224
00:13:14,590 --> 00:13:16,070
is not suited to eat.

225
00:13:16,630 --> 00:13:18,710
Fairies have no weight.

226
00:13:18,710 --> 00:13:21,790
I'll suspect that you're jealous.

227
00:13:21,790 --> 00:13:23,470
Who would I be jealous of?

228
00:13:23,910 --> 00:13:25,830
Would I be jealous of you destroying the
relationship of Jiang Yu Cheng and me?

229
00:13:29,230 --> 00:13:30,670
She hung up on me again!

230
00:13:35,790 --> 00:13:37,110
Oh, Er Gou.

231
00:13:37,110 --> 00:13:39,230
She only thinks about Jiang Yu Cheng now.

232
00:13:39,230 --> 00:13:40,670
She has forgotten us.

233
00:13:41,830 --> 00:13:43,510
It's so late and she's still not back.

234
00:13:59,350 --> 00:14:00,510
Er Gou.

235
00:14:04,350 --> 00:14:05,460
It's so late now.

236
00:14:05,460 --> 00:14:07,590
Why have you still not fed Er Gou?

237
00:14:08,030 --> 00:14:10,740
My pitiful Er Gou.

238
00:14:11,910 --> 00:14:12,990
I will feed you.

239
00:14:15,630 --> 00:14:16,550
Come.

240
00:14:20,750 --> 00:14:22,150
I also haven't eaten.

241
00:14:26,070 --> 00:14:27,430
Mr Zhou Chuan,

242
00:14:27,430 --> 00:14:28,270
ever since yesterday,

243
00:14:28,270 --> 00:14:29,990
you've been acting very strange.

244
00:14:29,990 --> 00:14:32,070
Your book is selling well.
Why are you so irritable?

245
00:14:32,070 --> 00:14:33,590
Who offended you?

246
00:14:33,590 --> 00:14:35,630
An ungrateful person hung up on me.

247
00:14:38,140 --> 00:14:40,630
I'll help you to teach her a lesson.

248
00:14:40,870 --> 00:14:42,100
I'll go make dinner.

249
00:14:42,350 --> 00:14:43,070
Wait.

250
00:14:45,870 --> 00:14:47,110
That...

251
00:14:48,830 --> 00:14:50,870
About the question that Jiang Yu Cheng
asked you yesterday.

252
00:14:52,100 --> 00:14:53,510
How much have you thought about it?

253
00:14:54,350 --> 00:14:56,070
I've clarified things with him.

254
00:14:58,830 --> 00:15:00,190
What did you clarify?

255
00:15:01,830 --> 00:15:02,780
Nothing much.

256
00:15:02,780 --> 00:15:04,030
You shouldn't care about this.

257
00:15:07,350 --> 00:15:09,030
Why is she blushing?

258
00:15:10,870 --> 00:15:12,230
Because of Jiang Yu Cheng?

259
00:15:17,630 --> 00:15:18,510
Chu Li!

260
00:15:20,150 --> 00:15:21,670
I heard that the Book of Luo He God

261
00:15:21,670 --> 00:15:23,230
is about to receive praise today.

262
00:15:23,700 --> 00:15:25,750
Ms Li, why are you here?

263
00:15:25,750 --> 00:15:27,790
I'm also a member
of the editorial department!

264
00:15:27,790 --> 00:15:30,300
I have to be here
during glorious time like this!

265
00:15:30,300 --> 00:15:31,950
There might even be awards.

266
00:15:32,430 --> 00:15:34,310
The Book of Luo He God sold so well.

267
00:15:34,310 --> 00:15:35,870
The prize money must be at least 5000!

268
00:15:35,870 --> 00:15:37,430
It might even be tens of thousands!

269
00:15:37,950 --> 00:15:41,590
I already think 5000 is a lot.
I didn't expect tens of thousands.

270
00:15:41,590 --> 00:15:43,150
Remember to treat us when the time comes!

271
00:15:43,910 --> 00:15:45,190
Miao said that

272
00:15:45,190 --> 00:15:46,390
if Book of Luo He God sells well,

273
00:15:46,390 --> 00:15:48,630
he will give you his position
as deputy editor.

274
00:15:49,750 --> 00:15:51,630
Let's go! I can't wait!

275
00:15:54,270 --> 00:15:56,190
See, even signs are being put up!

276
00:16:01,220 --> 00:16:03,070
Congratulations, Chu Li!

277
00:16:03,710 --> 00:16:05,030
It's only been just over half a year,

278
00:16:05,030 --> 00:16:07,510
and you've become the ace editor of
Yuan Yue Publishing House.

279
00:16:07,910 --> 00:16:08,990
See, I told you!

280
00:16:08,990 --> 00:16:11,070
Make sure to remember
the look on Miao's face.

281
00:16:11,070 --> 00:16:11,870
Bye!

282
00:16:11,870 --> 00:16:13,710
You had the luck to stand on
the giant's shoulder.

283
00:16:13,710 --> 00:16:15,950
With its support, you did an amazing job.

284
00:16:15,950 --> 00:16:17,110
Congratulations, Chu Li.

285
00:16:17,470 --> 00:16:19,110
Thank you, Xiao Niao.

286
00:16:19,110 --> 00:16:22,230
I hope you find a giant
which belongs to you soon too.

287
00:16:22,310 --> 00:16:23,100
[Book of Luo He God]

288
00:16:25,570 --> 00:16:27,940
[Book of Luo He God
Sales about to surpass]

289
00:16:30,190 --> 00:16:31,350
Come lend me a hand.

290
00:16:31,350 --> 00:16:32,070
Okay.

291
00:16:32,670 --> 00:16:34,780
Hello, can you all straighten this?

292
00:16:35,220 --> 00:16:37,710
Hello, who are you looking for?

293
00:16:38,300 --> 00:16:40,470
I'm here to meet Deputy Editor Miao.

294
00:16:46,630 --> 00:16:49,190
Hello, please have some warm water.

295
00:16:49,190 --> 00:16:51,270
I'm Chu Li from the editorial department.

296
00:16:51,270 --> 00:16:52,350
You are?

297
00:16:52,870 --> 00:16:54,030
Suo Heng.

298
00:16:55,230 --> 00:16:58,870
You're the author of Golden Spears and
Armoured Horses, Ms Suo Heng?

299
00:16:59,190 --> 00:17:00,230
You know about me?

300
00:17:00,910 --> 00:17:03,350
This book has a majestic writing style,

301
00:17:03,350 --> 00:17:04,910
with a tragic and heroic story.

302
00:17:04,910 --> 00:17:06,950
I thought it was written by a male author!

303
00:17:06,950 --> 00:17:09,390
I did not imagine it was written by
such a beauty.

304
00:17:10,230 --> 00:17:11,510
It's nothing like that.

305
00:17:11,510 --> 00:17:14,270
I only have this book which is
liked by a few people.

306
00:17:14,270 --> 00:17:16,950
How can that be? You're being too humble.

307
00:17:17,349 --> 00:17:19,270
You were here to meet
Deputy Editor Miao, right?

308
00:17:19,270 --> 00:17:20,390
I'll give him a call now,

309
00:17:20,390 --> 00:17:21,390
and ask where he is.

310
00:17:21,390 --> 00:17:22,349
Please wait for me.

311
00:17:24,390 --> 00:17:25,030
Hello?

312
00:17:25,030 --> 00:17:27,630
[Hello, Deputy Editor Miao?]
Where are you?

313
00:17:27,630 --> 00:17:29,390
Ms Suo Heng is here waiting for you.

314
00:17:30,589 --> 00:17:32,190
[Please tell Suo Heng.]

315
00:17:32,190 --> 00:17:33,470
[I have some things to handle outside]

316
00:17:33,470 --> 00:17:35,300
and won't be back to the
editorial department anytime soon.

317
00:17:35,670 --> 00:17:37,750
Never mind, just pass the phone to her.

318
00:17:37,750 --> 00:17:38,820
I'll explain it to her.

319
00:17:43,100 --> 00:17:44,590
Hello, Deputy Editor Miao?

320
00:17:44,590 --> 00:17:46,300
I've made some suitable amendments

321
00:17:46,300 --> 00:17:48,150
following what you told me.

322
00:17:48,150 --> 00:17:48,830
[Suo Heng,]

323
00:17:49,270 --> 00:17:50,870
I'll be frank with you.

324
00:17:52,270 --> 00:17:54,110
In your current condition,

325
00:17:54,110 --> 00:17:56,980
I understood the things
you've written before,

326
00:17:56,980 --> 00:17:59,710
but it's useless no matter how much
you changed.

327
00:18:00,430 --> 00:18:01,700
[How about this?]

328
00:18:01,700 --> 00:18:04,830
[I'll send over some authors' works
for you to read in a bit.]

329
00:18:04,830 --> 00:18:06,590
[Take a look at them and reflect]

330
00:18:06,590 --> 00:18:07,830
[before you continue writing.]

331
00:18:07,830 --> 00:18:08,590
We'll move forward like this.

332
00:18:08,590 --> 00:18:10,270
I'm busy handling some matters.

333
00:18:10,270 --> 00:18:11,990
Let's end here.
[Bye!]

334
00:18:11,990 --> 00:18:13,110
Miao...

335
00:18:20,510 --> 00:18:23,060
I'll leave now. I'm sorry.

336
00:18:23,990 --> 00:18:24,750
Suo...

337
00:18:25,990 --> 00:18:26,790
Mum,

338
00:18:27,020 --> 00:18:28,590
Li Wei has guaranteed me

339
00:18:28,590 --> 00:18:29,790
that he will be back

340
00:18:29,790 --> 00:18:31,190
before Qiu Qiu's Sports' Day.

341
00:18:31,190 --> 00:18:33,150
Ms Suo Heng, please hold on!

342
00:18:40,220 --> 00:18:42,030
Ms Suo Heng! Ms...

343
00:18:46,550 --> 00:18:48,310
That Deputy Editor Miao is really bad.

344
00:18:48,470 --> 00:18:49,790
How can he dump someone here

345
00:18:49,790 --> 00:18:51,430
with just a call?

346
00:18:55,150 --> 00:18:56,390
Chu Li.

347
00:18:58,110 --> 00:18:59,630
Do your work well.

348
00:18:59,630 --> 00:19:01,150
Don't let your author down.

349
00:19:01,870 --> 00:19:03,790
Book of Luo He God is making
a name for itself.

350
00:19:03,790 --> 00:19:05,350
Jiang Yu Cheng even gave you
his new book to you.

351
00:19:05,350 --> 00:19:06,670
You need to continue your good work.

352
00:19:07,180 --> 00:19:09,590
If Jiang Yu Cheng can rise from the ashes,

353
00:19:09,590 --> 00:19:11,910
it will also serve as a ray of hope

354
00:19:11,910 --> 00:19:13,270
for authors who are currently in a slump.

355
00:19:16,470 --> 00:19:17,950
I will do my best.

356
00:19:20,060 --> 00:19:20,500
Director Gu,

357
00:19:20,500 --> 00:19:22,260
this is the list of authors who will
participate in the Book Exchange.

358
00:19:22,260 --> 00:19:23,230
Please take a look.

359
00:19:29,950 --> 00:19:30,990
Is Jiang Yu Cheng not attending?

360
00:19:31,390 --> 00:19:32,700
Jiang Yu Cheng has contacted us,

361
00:19:32,700 --> 00:19:33,910
but he said he would not attend.

362
00:19:34,950 --> 00:19:35,870
Put his name on the list.

363
00:19:35,870 --> 00:19:37,220
I'll follow up on this matter myself.

364
00:19:37,470 --> 00:19:37,910
Okay.

365
00:19:38,790 --> 00:19:39,980
There's another thing.

366
00:19:40,990 --> 00:19:42,750
Yun Fei's book has been on hiatus
for three days already.

367
00:19:42,750 --> 00:19:43,710
We couldn't contact him.

368
00:19:45,150 --> 00:19:46,350
Have you been to his house?

369
00:19:46,350 --> 00:19:47,830
We've been there. No one was in.

370
00:19:49,550 --> 00:19:50,420
I'll handle it.

371
00:20:01,830 --> 00:20:04,550
[Hello, the caller you are dialling
is currently switched off.]

372
00:20:04,550 --> 00:20:06,270
[Please dial again shortly.]

373
00:20:35,420 --> 00:20:36,790
How did you find me?

374
00:20:37,910 --> 00:20:40,150
You always play here
whenever you're unhappy.

375
00:20:40,750 --> 00:20:42,150
You should find somewhere new.

376
00:20:45,780 --> 00:20:47,070
Tell me. What's wrong?

377
00:20:50,910 --> 00:20:52,310
When something happened to Ms Liu
the other day,

378
00:20:54,580 --> 00:20:56,070
you just cried in front of him.

379
00:20:56,710 --> 00:20:57,910
Before he arrived,

380
00:20:57,910 --> 00:20:59,390
I was always by your side.

381
00:21:00,870 --> 00:21:02,230
Am I so unreliable?

382
00:21:03,110 --> 00:21:04,260
Just because of this?

383
00:21:06,270 --> 00:21:07,460
Of course not.

384
00:21:09,390 --> 00:21:10,750
Both Jiang Yu Cheng and I

385
00:21:10,750 --> 00:21:12,390
write mystery stories.

386
00:21:13,350 --> 00:21:14,630
When my first book was published,

387
00:21:14,630 --> 00:21:16,700
some people called me
a mini Jiang Yu Cheng.

388
00:21:19,470 --> 00:21:20,310
Fine.

389
00:21:21,030 --> 00:21:22,910
So, I avoided modern stories.

390
00:21:22,910 --> 00:21:24,150
I wrote stories about the past.

391
00:21:25,310 --> 00:21:27,750
I just don't want to be called
a mini Jiang Yu Cheng.

392
00:21:28,710 --> 00:21:29,790
But Ms Liu...

393
00:21:30,750 --> 00:21:32,310
When she met me that day,

394
00:21:32,310 --> 00:21:33,190
she also called me Xiao Jiang.

395
00:21:34,470 --> 00:21:35,870
Then you got drunk,

396
00:21:36,110 --> 00:21:37,550
held onto my hand

397
00:21:37,550 --> 00:21:38,630
and called out his name.

398
00:21:46,870 --> 00:21:48,500
I am not a mini Jiang Yu Cheng.

399
00:21:49,190 --> 00:21:50,390
I am Yun Fei.

400
00:21:54,510 --> 00:21:57,350
You're clear about
the situation I'm in, right?

401
00:21:58,310 --> 00:21:59,350
That day,

402
00:21:59,750 --> 00:22:01,670
I really was drunk.

403
00:22:02,030 --> 00:22:03,030
I'm sorry.

404
00:22:04,670 --> 00:22:07,790
No one sees you as just a replacement.

405
00:22:07,790 --> 00:22:09,630
What's the point of

406
00:22:09,630 --> 00:22:11,030
driving yourself into a dead end?

407
00:22:12,150 --> 00:22:13,950
I don't know where you got

408
00:22:13,950 --> 00:22:15,340
such messy thoughts from.

409
00:22:16,030 --> 00:22:17,190
But no matter where they're from,

410
00:22:17,190 --> 00:22:18,310
you have to dispose of them.

411
00:22:24,470 --> 00:22:26,900
What's most important to you
right now is writing.

412
00:22:27,590 --> 00:22:29,420
Don't forget that when
spring comes next year,

413
00:22:30,070 --> 00:22:32,270
you and Jiang Yu Cheng will publish
new stories at the same time.

414
00:22:33,470 --> 00:22:35,750
Don't you want to stop being called
a mini Jiang Yu Cheng?

415
00:22:37,310 --> 00:22:39,190
If you beat him,
he will be the mini Yun Fei.

416
00:22:44,470 --> 00:22:45,270
Sister.

417
00:22:47,390 --> 00:22:48,510
Do you think I can do it?

418
00:22:48,710 --> 00:22:49,870
Of course.

419
00:22:50,910 --> 00:22:53,790
How can someone scouted by me ever lose?

420
00:22:57,270 --> 00:22:58,190
Alright.

421
00:22:59,510 --> 00:23:00,750
I'll be going back to write.

422
00:23:01,110 --> 00:23:02,150
Go.

423
00:23:04,390 --> 00:23:04,950
For you.

424
00:23:05,470 --> 00:23:06,350
Thank you.

425
00:23:10,830 --> 00:23:13,340
[I've recently been reading
Zhou Chuan's Book of Luo He God.]

426
00:23:10,840 --> 00:23:29,890
[The Navy Hired by the Monkey]

427
00:23:13,340 --> 00:23:15,150
[Through this masterpiece,]

428
00:23:15,150 --> 00:23:18,030
[I've definitely come in contact with
an interesting soul.]

429
00:23:18,030 --> 00:23:19,870
[And it's one in a million.]

430
00:23:19,870 --> 00:23:22,270
[All the complaints you've had of him]

431
00:23:22,270 --> 00:23:24,030
[are clearly your biases showing.]

432
00:23:24,030 --> 00:23:26,950
[I've discovered that he's even more
outstanding than Jiang Yu Cheng.]

433
00:23:27,310 --> 00:23:29,990
[You're really a poor judge of people.]

434
00:23:29,890 --> 00:23:37,190
[The Disappearing Mr Fox]

435
00:23:29,990 --> 00:23:31,870
[Thank you for your confidence
in this book.]

436
00:23:31,870 --> 00:23:33,470
[I'm extremely honoured.]

437
00:23:33,470 --> 00:23:35,790
[But an interesting soul and a toxic soul]

438
00:23:35,790 --> 00:23:37,190
[are fundamentally different.]

439
00:23:38,070 --> 00:23:40,590
She has the nerve to say my soul is toxic?

440
00:23:44,980 --> 00:23:58,880
[The Navy Hired by the Monkey]

441
00:23:45,830 --> 00:23:48,550
[Even Zhou Chuan
is uninteresting for you.]

442
00:23:48,550 --> 00:23:50,350
[You must have a really high standard.]

443
00:23:53,390 --> 00:23:55,110
[So, what are your standards
in choosing a partner?]

444
00:23:55,110 --> 00:23:56,910
[Someone like Jiang Yu Cheng?]

445
00:23:57,270 --> 00:23:59,270
[Do all girls like phoney men like him?]

446
00:24:00,150 --> 00:24:01,980
What's up with Mr Fox?

447
00:24:01,980 --> 00:24:03,790
He keeps asking these weird questions.

448
00:24:03,790 --> 00:24:06,110
My standard of a partner,
is it Jiang Yu...

449
00:24:06,110 --> 00:24:06,990
Chu Li,

450
00:24:07,310 --> 00:24:09,230
Hurry, look at the email!

451
00:24:07,460 --> 00:24:09,220
[Yes]

452
00:24:09,220 --> 00:24:12,170
[The Navy Hired by the Monkey]

453
00:24:09,870 --> 00:24:10,710
[Yes.]

454
00:24:12,540 --> 00:24:13,300
You're here too?

455
00:24:13,300 --> 00:24:14,470
I was thinking about inviting you.

456
00:24:17,820 --> 00:24:19,430
I don't like the way you played it.

457
00:24:19,430 --> 00:24:20,310
What's up with you?

458
00:24:20,310 --> 00:24:21,310
Are you not going to use a racket?

459
00:24:21,310 --> 00:24:22,350
Don't talk so much.

460
00:24:22,350 --> 00:24:23,470
I'll be playing against you.

461
00:24:46,270 --> 00:24:47,710
Ever since graduating from high school,

462
00:24:47,710 --> 00:24:49,150
I haven't played

463
00:24:49,150 --> 00:24:50,590
such a fun match of squash with you.

464
00:24:50,750 --> 00:24:52,260
You asked to be tortured.

465
00:24:54,110 --> 00:24:55,670
When do you plan on telling Chu Li

466
00:24:55,670 --> 00:24:56,750
that you are her online friend?

467
00:24:57,790 --> 00:24:59,070
I don't plan to tell her.

468
00:25:00,630 --> 00:25:01,940
Why are you suddenly asking about this?

469
00:25:04,260 --> 00:25:08,100
[I'm honoured that you like me.]

470
00:25:08,100 --> 00:25:10,030
[However,]

471
00:25:10,030 --> 00:25:12,910
[I already have someone I like.]

472
00:25:13,390 --> 00:25:14,270
[Who is it?]

473
00:25:14,750 --> 00:25:15,430
[Zhou Chuan?]

474
00:25:16,630 --> 00:25:17,390
[It's...]

475
00:25:18,340 --> 00:25:21,830
[It's a friend online I made
a long time ago.]

476
00:25:21,830 --> 00:25:23,430
[His name is Mr Fox.]

477
00:25:26,190 --> 00:25:27,310
[Mr Fox?]

478
00:25:28,070 --> 00:25:29,390
[So, does this Mr Fox]

479
00:25:29,390 --> 00:25:31,590
[know about your feelings?]

480
00:25:31,590 --> 00:25:32,390
[Does he also like you?]

481
00:25:33,790 --> 00:25:35,310
[I'm not very sure either.]

482
00:25:36,430 --> 00:25:39,030
[Anyway, I'm sorry, Mr Jiang.]

483
00:25:43,100 --> 00:25:45,070
You've always been

484
00:25:45,070 --> 00:25:46,550
an awkward

485
00:25:46,550 --> 00:25:47,270
and indirect person since young.

486
00:25:49,790 --> 00:25:51,310
I can't hear what you're saying.

487
00:25:51,990 --> 00:25:52,710
Speaking of being awkward,

488
00:25:52,710 --> 00:25:54,070
some people really are dense.

489
00:25:54,710 --> 00:25:56,670
Just like a drowning person finding
a piece of driftwood,

490
00:25:56,670 --> 00:25:57,790
then claiming it as his own.

491
00:25:57,790 --> 00:25:59,590
When seeing a good umbrella
on a rainy day,

492
00:25:59,790 --> 00:26:01,510
he wants to snatch it out
from others' hands.

493
00:26:03,950 --> 00:26:05,910
She's been quietly supporting me
all these years.

494
00:26:06,310 --> 00:26:07,750
It's quite unclear

495
00:26:07,750 --> 00:26:08,740
that who will be the winner.

496
00:26:08,740 --> 00:26:10,630
Someone like Gu Bai Zhi suits you.

497
00:26:11,070 --> 00:26:12,510
Don't trouble Chu Li.

498
00:26:12,510 --> 00:26:13,510
Stay away from her.

499
00:26:19,990 --> 00:26:21,230
Whether or not we're suitable,

500
00:26:21,230 --> 00:26:22,230
I'm very clear about that.

501
00:26:23,550 --> 00:26:25,230
You aren't being jealous, right?

502
00:26:28,100 --> 00:26:29,270
What would I be jealous of you?

503
00:26:29,470 --> 00:26:30,860
What would I be jealous of you?

504
00:26:31,150 --> 00:26:32,270
Are your sales better than mine?

505
00:26:32,270 --> 00:26:33,430
Or are you more popular than me?

506
00:26:34,030 --> 00:26:35,030
I'm warning you.

507
00:26:35,030 --> 00:26:37,630
I'm Yuan Ye Publishing House's
ace author now.

508
00:26:37,630 --> 00:26:38,780
If you get on my nerves,

509
00:26:38,780 --> 00:26:40,630
I'll make them
end their contract with you.

510
00:26:45,290 --> 00:26:46,910
[All employees of Yuan Publishing：]

511
00:26:46,910 --> 00:26:48,280
[Mr Liang Chong Lang has been chosen
to receive the "Best Employee" award]

512
00:26:48,280 --> 00:26:49,160
[and a cash bonus of 5000 yuan.]

513
00:26:51,750 --> 00:26:53,190
Dear colleagues.

514
00:26:54,270 --> 00:26:56,390
Mr Liang has bought coffee for everyone.

515
00:26:56,870 --> 00:26:59,070
The sales for Book of Luo He God

