00:26:59,070 --> 00:27:02,030
have hit 349,000 copies!

517
00:27:02,030 --> 00:27:03,830
This is the best result in
Yuan Yue Publishing House's

518
00:27:03,830 --> 00:27:04,860
five year history.

519
00:27:05,350 --> 00:27:06,510
The circulation department

520
00:27:06,510 --> 00:27:08,820
is extremely grateful for the support
from our editorial colleagues.

521
00:27:08,820 --> 00:27:10,110
Enjoy.

522
00:27:15,150 --> 00:27:17,510
After waiting so long,
we only got a cup of coffee?

523
00:27:17,830 --> 00:27:19,550
Mr Liang's sales figures this time

524
00:27:19,550 --> 00:27:21,070
are just too strange, right?

525
00:27:21,470 --> 00:27:23,460
349,000 copies.

526
00:27:23,710 --> 00:27:25,950
With just another 1000 copies,
it would have been 350,000.

527
00:27:27,190 --> 00:27:28,910
Deputy Editor Miao's spot

528
00:27:28,910 --> 00:27:30,430
is about to be yours.

529
00:27:30,430 --> 00:27:32,700
Chu Li, what a pity.

530
00:27:36,950 --> 00:27:38,190
Who's speaking right now?

531
00:27:41,630 --> 00:27:42,750
Isn't this

532
00:27:42,750 --> 00:27:44,430
Sis Xian Yu who enjoys disappearing?

533
00:27:45,140 --> 00:27:46,830
Editor Xian Yu,

534
00:27:46,830 --> 00:27:49,950
do you think that my role
as a deputy editor

535
00:27:49,950 --> 00:27:51,350
can be given to whoever you like?

536
00:27:51,670 --> 00:27:54,030
That will depend on
the rules of our organisation.

537
00:27:54,190 --> 00:27:55,260
I think that

538
00:27:55,260 --> 00:27:56,670
you're not here to work,

539
00:27:56,670 --> 00:27:58,430
but you're just here for a show, right?

540
00:28:02,030 --> 00:28:03,790
My hip hurts!

541
00:28:04,190 --> 00:28:06,790
Sisters, keep up the good work.

542
00:28:06,790 --> 00:28:08,230
I'm going back to rest.

543
00:28:10,220 --> 00:28:11,790
Goodbye, Sis Xian Yu.

544
00:28:11,790 --> 00:28:12,870
Goodbye.

545
00:28:14,510 --> 00:28:16,590
This is too unfair, right?

546
00:28:16,590 --> 00:28:19,070
Not a single word is used to credit
us from the editorial department.

