In future, our editorial department

548
00:28:21,070 --> 00:28:23,830
is going to carry even less weight before
those of the circulation department.

549
00:28:24,470 --> 00:28:26,470
I originally wanted to

550
00:28:26,470 --> 00:28:29,550
use the prize money to change my glasses.

551
00:28:29,550 --> 00:28:31,900
Now I can't change them.

552
00:28:33,710 --> 00:28:34,590
Ah Xiang.

553
00:28:35,590 --> 00:28:37,670
Are the wages from the firm

554
00:28:37,670 --> 00:28:40,070
not even enough for you to change
your glasses?

555
00:28:41,110 --> 00:28:42,510
What are you complaining about?

556
00:28:42,990 --> 00:28:44,670
We're all from Yuan Yue Publishing House.

557
00:28:44,990 --> 00:28:46,100
Those in the circulation department

558
00:28:46,100 --> 00:28:49,310
spend all day looking at
advertising and sales.

559
00:28:49,310 --> 00:28:50,470
Their job is not easy too.

560
00:28:50,470 --> 00:28:52,630
You can't blame them for
receiving a prize.

561
00:28:52,990 --> 00:28:55,910
We worked very hard too.

562
00:28:58,470 --> 00:28:59,870
This is precisely my point.

563
00:29:00,180 --> 00:29:01,750
We're lucky

564
00:29:01,750 --> 00:29:03,580
if we find people like Zhou Chuan

565
00:29:03,830 --> 00:29:05,190
who bring in their own readers.

566
00:29:06,830 --> 00:29:07,950
As an editor,

567
00:29:08,710 --> 00:29:09,950
we shouldn't be surprised

568
00:29:10,230 --> 00:29:11,990
if a book like this sell well.

569
00:29:11,990 --> 00:29:13,870
If it's unable to sell well,
that's a true achievement.

570
00:29:16,950 --> 00:29:18,990
Once Mr Zhou Xuan publicised
the story online,

571
00:29:18,990 --> 00:29:21,190
the shares by readers
were over 10,000 in an hour.

572
00:29:21,190 --> 00:29:22,710
Let's not think about superstars.

573
00:29:23,180 --> 00:29:24,820
But among authors,

574
00:29:24,820 --> 00:29:25,990
this sort of influence is rare.

575
00:29:26,350 --> 00:29:28,020
That's why I'm saying,

576
00:29:28,340 --> 00:29:29,870
you as an editor

577
00:29:30,220 --> 00:29:32,670
being able to sell so many books
in such a short time

578
00:29:33,030 --> 00:29:34,550
has nothing to do with your ability.

579
00:29:34,550 --> 00:29:36,070
It was just a matter of good luck.

580
00:29:36,070 --> 00:29:39,110
People were praising the subscription
letter of the new editor as well-written,

581
00:29:39,110 --> 00:29:41,070
but what do sales have
to do with the letter?

582
00:29:41,780 --> 00:29:44,300
Maybe no one even read what she wrote.

583
00:29:44,860 --> 00:29:46,830
People only know that
its Zhou Chuan's book.

584
00:29:46,830 --> 00:29:48,950
So, they just blindly add

585
00:29:48,950 --> 00:29:51,070
a few zeroes behind their orders.

586
00:29:56,110 --> 00:29:58,030
Since you're sure that
Mr Zhou Xuan's sales

587
00:29:58,030 --> 00:29:59,790
will be good,

588
00:29:59,790 --> 00:30:01,390
why Deputy Editor Miao, you were unwilling

589
00:30:01,390 --> 00:30:03,710
to increase the value of the contract?

590
00:30:04,660 --> 00:30:06,390
Book of Luo He God sold so well.

591
00:30:06,390 --> 00:30:07,950
Even a mere 200 copies

592
00:30:07,950 --> 00:30:10,710
were related to the subscription letter
that I edited many times,

593
00:30:11,110 --> 00:30:13,910
I was still the one who managed
to make his sign contact with us

594
00:30:13,910 --> 00:30:16,100
even with our small amount
of guaranteed printing.

595
00:30:16,100 --> 00:30:17,190
Chu Li.

596
00:30:18,790 --> 00:30:20,060
Are you not satisfied
with my criticism?

597
00:30:20,060 --> 00:30:21,190
Is your ego so inflated?

598
00:30:22,030 --> 00:30:23,630
Do you speak to your superior like this?

599
00:30:23,630 --> 00:30:25,230
What kind of attitude is this?

600
00:30:25,990 --> 00:30:27,470
Living off peoples' glory,

601
00:30:27,470 --> 00:30:28,630
is this your skill?

602
00:30:29,300 --> 00:30:31,430
Standing on a house someone else built,

603
00:30:31,430 --> 00:30:33,510
showing off shamelessly, is this skill?

604
00:30:33,950 --> 00:30:34,590
If you have the skill,

605
00:30:34,590 --> 00:30:36,460
you should build your own house!

606
00:30:38,750 --> 00:30:40,390
Our editorial department

607
00:30:40,390 --> 00:30:41,830
did not receive a commendation this time.

608
00:30:42,590 --> 00:30:44,150
I'll say this to all of you.

609
00:30:45,030 --> 00:30:48,430
"It is through work that we improve,
and all efforts will be repaid one day."

610
00:30:50,630 --> 00:30:53,270
Okay, the quadrennial Huazhi Award

611
00:30:53,270 --> 00:30:54,750
have begun judging again.

612
00:30:54,750 --> 00:30:55,550
If the material submitted by

613
00:30:55,550 --> 00:30:58,110
our editorial department can win a prize,

614
00:30:58,110 --> 00:31:00,870
no one can take this honour away from us.

615
00:31:02,790 --> 00:31:03,980
The Huazhi Award.

616
00:31:03,980 --> 00:31:06,750
So, Mr Xia, which work from
our editorial department

617
00:31:06,750 --> 00:31:09,070
do you intend to push forward?

618
00:31:10,190 --> 00:31:13,220
From the first section,
there's The Edge from Mr Chu,

619
00:31:13,220 --> 00:31:15,590
and Daybreak from Ms Zheng.

620
00:31:16,510 --> 00:31:19,190
For the second department, there's
science fiction work from He Ma,

621
00:31:19,190 --> 00:31:20,260
The Earth.

622
00:31:21,580 --> 00:31:22,990
Mr He Ma

623
00:31:22,990 --> 00:31:24,510
is a good author.

624
00:31:24,510 --> 00:31:26,710
The chance of winning will be very high.

625
00:31:28,270 --> 00:31:30,870
And, Book of Luo He God from Zhou Chuan.

626
00:31:31,750 --> 00:31:33,030
Book of Luo He God.

627
00:31:34,150 --> 00:31:34,990
Mr Xia,

628
00:31:34,990 --> 00:31:36,310
Huazhi Award

629
00:31:36,310 --> 00:31:38,950
is an award for serious
traditional literature.

630
00:31:39,630 --> 00:31:41,230
Although Zhou Chuan's book

631
00:31:41,670 --> 00:31:43,260
is a traditional legend,

632
00:31:43,260 --> 00:31:45,990
it has quite a lot of
fantasy elements, right?

633
00:31:45,990 --> 00:31:47,550
Maybe...

634
00:31:47,550 --> 00:31:49,590
Times are changing.

635
00:31:49,590 --> 00:31:52,110
Even the old heads judges

636
00:31:52,110 --> 00:31:53,070
should know that it's time

637
00:31:53,070 --> 00:31:56,340
to accept the modern trends.

638
00:31:56,900 --> 00:31:58,150
And we should also

639
00:31:58,150 --> 00:32:00,390
keep up with this trend.

640
00:32:02,030 --> 00:32:03,060
Chu Li,

641
00:32:03,230 --> 00:32:05,270
check on Mr Zhou Chuan's
opinion immediately.

642
00:32:05,590 --> 00:32:06,070
Okay.

643
00:32:06,260 --> 00:32:08,830
If Zhou Chuan has a conflict of emotion,

644
00:32:09,190 --> 00:32:09,910
remember,

645
00:32:10,550 --> 00:32:13,030
heroes struggle to deal with beauties.

646
00:32:16,150 --> 00:32:17,670
Whether or not Chu Li is a beauty
is yet to be seen.

647
00:32:17,670 --> 00:32:19,670
But, she will give it a try.

648
00:32:20,750 --> 00:32:22,100
Don't worry, Mr Xia.

649
00:32:22,100 --> 00:32:23,910
A matter like this where he can
receive honour

650
00:32:23,910 --> 00:32:25,910
should not cause him any conflict.

651
00:32:36,430 --> 00:32:37,430
Hello, what's up?

652
00:32:38,150 --> 00:32:39,310
Mr Zhou Chuan,

653
00:32:39,310 --> 00:32:41,910
from your voice,
I guess you're not in a good mood.

654
00:32:42,150 --> 00:32:43,070
I'm hanging up if there's nothing.

655
00:32:43,510 --> 00:32:45,350
There's something!

656
00:32:45,510 --> 00:32:46,270
Mr Zhou Chuan,

657
00:32:46,270 --> 00:32:48,470
Mr Xia brought up Huazhi Award today.

658
00:32:48,470 --> 00:32:50,380
You should know about it, right?

659
00:32:51,030 --> 00:32:53,590
You want to submit
Book of Luo He God for the award?

660
00:32:54,310 --> 00:32:56,150
Impossible. I'm not going!

661
00:32:58,630 --> 00:32:59,350
Hello?

662
00:33:04,710 --> 00:33:05,390
Chu Li.

663
00:33:06,030 --> 00:33:06,870
It's hot.

664
00:33:07,310 --> 00:33:09,790
Ah Xiang, I finally know

665
00:33:09,790 --> 00:33:10,710
why Mr Xia

666
00:33:10,710 --> 00:33:12,750
wanted me to desperately
ask Mr Zhou Chuan

667
00:33:12,750 --> 00:33:14,260
about Huazhi Award.

668
00:33:14,260 --> 00:33:16,340
Ginger gets spicier the older it gets.

669
00:33:16,340 --> 00:33:18,350
Mr Zhou Chuan was very steadfast
in his decision

670
00:33:18,350 --> 00:33:19,980
to not submit his work to
participate in the Huazhi Award.

671
00:33:19,980 --> 00:33:21,150
I can't understand.

672
00:33:21,150 --> 00:33:23,790
Why someone would avoid honours so much?

673
00:33:23,790 --> 00:33:25,390
You don't need to be so anxious.

674
00:33:26,030 --> 00:33:27,140
I think that you should

675
00:33:27,140 --> 00:33:29,590
have a good talk with Mr Zhou Chuan.

676
00:33:29,590 --> 00:33:32,590
This matter doesn't only involve him,

677
00:33:32,590 --> 00:33:34,180
but also Mr Xia.

678
00:33:34,590 --> 00:33:35,820
Why?

679
00:33:36,550 --> 00:33:37,700
Last time when Mr Xia

680
00:33:37,700 --> 00:33:40,710
was in charge of Time Is Like A Song
from Old Mr Zhou,

681
00:33:40,710 --> 00:33:43,590
he still wanted to improve it.

682
00:33:43,590 --> 00:33:46,790
In the end, the book did
not win in Huazhi Award.

683
00:33:46,790 --> 00:33:48,700
And so by mistake,

684
00:33:48,700 --> 00:33:51,150
it was awarded to another book.

685
00:33:52,190 --> 00:33:53,710
This kind of thing happened?

686
00:33:54,980 --> 00:33:57,620
Has he never sent a book
for judging since then?

687
00:33:58,150 --> 00:33:59,110
He did.

688
00:33:59,110 --> 00:34:00,910
In the past years of Huazhi Award,

689
00:34:00,910 --> 00:34:04,190
all the books handled by Mr Xia
were submitted.

690
00:34:04,190 --> 00:34:06,830
But they were only given
honourable mentions.

691
00:34:06,830 --> 00:34:08,310
He was snubbed again and again.

692
00:34:08,750 --> 00:34:10,380
And people started to call him

693
00:34:10,380 --> 00:34:13,150
the Murakami of the editorial world.

694
00:34:14,659 --> 00:34:17,030
Being snubbed for 20 years?

695
00:34:17,550 --> 00:34:19,830
No wonder Mr Xia is so vocal about

696
00:34:19,830 --> 00:34:21,699
how he owes Yuan Yue Publishing House
a Huazhi Award.

697
00:34:21,699 --> 00:34:24,870
If I were him, I would
be determined to get it too.

698
00:34:24,870 --> 00:34:25,900
Yes.

699
00:34:25,900 --> 00:34:28,909
This might be Mr Xia's last chance

700
00:34:29,150 --> 00:34:30,550
before he retires.

701
00:34:32,230 --> 00:34:34,750
[How can I convince Zhou Chuan?]

702
00:34:48,949 --> 00:34:49,949
Don't leave.

703
00:34:54,750 --> 00:34:56,310
I'm here to talk to you about work.

704
00:35:03,670 --> 00:35:05,230
A lot of your old friends

705
00:35:05,940 --> 00:35:07,230
will be attending
Xin Dun Creative Exchange.

706
00:35:08,950 --> 00:35:09,870
I'm sorry.

707
00:35:10,590 --> 00:35:12,190
I've already told your company.

708
00:35:12,390 --> 00:35:13,420
I'm busy.

709
00:35:13,590 --> 00:35:14,420
You have time.

710
00:35:15,270 --> 00:35:16,390
You just don't want to go.

711
00:35:20,070 --> 00:35:20,670
It's better for you to interact more

712
00:35:20,670 --> 00:35:22,710
in the authors' circle.

713
00:35:22,710 --> 00:35:24,030
There are many things that
you will not learn about

714
00:35:24,030 --> 00:35:25,030
if you stay in this bookstore.

715
00:35:26,150 --> 00:35:27,620
If in the future,

716
00:35:27,620 --> 00:35:29,150
you wish to leave
Yuan Yue Publishing House,

717
00:35:29,150 --> 00:35:31,430
and want to find a new editor,
and a new publishing house,

718
00:35:32,350 --> 00:35:33,990
those information will be useful for you.

719
00:35:39,430 --> 00:35:42,330
[Xin Dun Creative Exchange]

720
00:35:55,750 --> 00:35:56,950
Who's there?

721
00:36:15,700 --> 00:36:16,670
Mr Liang,

722
00:36:17,070 --> 00:36:18,900
I need to thank you for
that previous matter.

723
00:36:19,270 --> 00:36:21,430
About the number 349,000,

724
00:36:21,830 --> 00:36:22,670
I understand your meaning.

725
00:36:24,230 --> 00:36:25,710
Please don't mind that I criticise you.

726
00:36:25,870 --> 00:36:27,190
You're already old.

727
00:36:27,190 --> 00:36:29,270
You shouldn't speak so inappropriately

728
00:36:29,270 --> 00:36:30,950
in front of a little girl.

729
00:36:31,870 --> 00:36:33,390
You almost threw away your position.

730
00:36:34,550 --> 00:36:36,470
I was too careless.

731
00:36:36,470 --> 00:36:37,590
Who knew that Zhou Chuan's book

732
00:36:37,590 --> 00:36:39,790
would be able to sell so well?

733
00:36:40,270 --> 00:36:41,230
It's fine now.

734
00:36:41,790 --> 00:36:43,430
Chu Li

735
00:36:43,870 --> 00:36:45,190
is even more arrogant and domineering.

736
00:36:45,910 --> 00:36:47,620
Why does she dare to act this way?

737
00:36:48,230 --> 00:36:50,510
It's because you're the deputy editor.

738
00:36:51,070 --> 00:36:53,390
Yu Yao is the chief editor.

739
00:36:53,590 --> 00:36:55,550
She's supporting the little girl.

740
00:36:55,550 --> 00:36:57,950
Would she respect you?

741
00:37:01,190 --> 00:37:02,350
Miao,

742
00:37:02,910 --> 00:37:04,350
have you ever thought of

743
00:37:04,670 --> 00:37:07,420
a promotion?

744
00:37:13,390 --> 00:37:15,710
There's nothing special about

745
00:37:16,020 --> 00:37:17,430
the role of chief editor.

746
00:37:18,790 --> 00:37:19,790
Look,

747
00:37:19,790 --> 00:37:22,470
the wages don't increase much.

748
00:37:23,670 --> 00:37:25,430
The workload and responsibilities

749
00:37:25,430 --> 00:37:27,230
increase substantially instead.

750
00:37:27,230 --> 00:37:29,710
Unlike now, I'm a deputy editor

751
00:37:29,710 --> 00:37:30,860
and I'm still relatively relaxed.

752
00:37:31,270 --> 00:37:32,790
You can continue to act.

753
00:37:32,790 --> 00:37:33,830
You continue acting before me.

754
00:37:35,190 --> 00:37:37,510
If you want to relax, it's easy.

755
00:37:38,110 --> 00:37:39,830
If you relax, you will also
be taken advantage of.

756
00:37:43,030 --> 00:37:43,860
Miao.

757
00:37:45,070 --> 00:37:45,830
Thank you.

758
00:37:46,910 --> 00:37:47,820
Think about it.

759
00:37:48,670 --> 00:37:50,750
If you become the chief editor,

760
00:37:50,750 --> 00:37:53,310
who at Yuan Yue Publishing House
will dare to take advantage of you?

761
00:37:53,710 --> 00:37:55,030
Think of it in another way.

762
00:37:55,350 --> 00:37:57,500
If you don't want
to work at Yuan Yue Publishing House

763
00:37:57,500 --> 00:37:59,140
and want go to some other big company,

764
00:37:59,140 --> 00:38:01,510
if you go with the role of chief editor,

765
00:38:01,510 --> 00:38:02,780
you will at least be a director, right?

766
00:38:03,310 --> 00:38:04,830
If you remain in your role
as a deputy editor,

767
00:38:04,950 --> 00:38:07,790
you'll only be offered a manager position.

768
00:38:08,230 --> 00:38:10,990
I'm sure you're clear of how

769
00:38:10,990 --> 00:38:12,900
power is distributed among
those in charge here.

770
00:38:13,430 --> 00:38:14,550
Of course.

771
00:38:14,550 --> 00:38:16,980
This is your personal matter.

772
00:38:17,230 --> 00:38:18,350
I won't force you.

773
00:38:22,750 --> 00:38:24,510
I agree with you.

774
00:38:24,950 --> 00:38:26,470
But,

775
00:38:26,470 --> 00:38:29,670
Yu Yao was handpicked by Mr Xia.

776
00:38:30,150 --> 00:38:31,270
Although she used to be busy

777
00:38:31,270 --> 00:38:33,070
handling matters at home,

778
00:38:33,700 --> 00:38:36,510
in terms of her work,

779
00:38:36,510 --> 00:38:38,420
there aren't any major flaws.

780
00:38:38,790 --> 00:38:39,470
So...

781
00:38:42,270 --> 00:38:43,710
During the cultural exchange event,

782
00:38:43,710 --> 00:38:47,900
wasn't there an author called Suo Heng?

783
00:38:47,900 --> 00:38:50,630
She's a good friend of Yu Yao.

784
00:38:51,990 --> 00:38:53,270
This Suo Heng.

785
00:38:53,430 --> 00:38:55,590
I wanted to use this matter

786
00:38:55,590 --> 00:38:56,790
to make her leave.

787
00:38:57,580 --> 00:38:58,790
How was her sales?

788
00:38:58,790 --> 00:39:00,470
If her sales were good,

789
00:39:00,470 --> 00:39:02,310
how could I let her leave?

790
00:39:02,550 --> 00:39:05,150
Didn't Director Yang say
during the meeting,

791
00:39:05,270 --> 00:39:06,820
writers with poor sales

792
00:39:06,820 --> 00:39:07,950
must be dealt with without consideration?

793
00:39:08,260 --> 00:39:11,310
He repeated that their contracts
have to be nullified,

794
00:39:11,630 --> 00:39:12,630
am I right?

795
00:39:18,700 --> 00:39:20,140
What kind of person is Yu Yao?

796
00:39:21,270 --> 00:39:23,110
She's someone who values loyalty, right?

797
00:39:23,430 --> 00:39:25,390
This is something she's always stressed.

798
00:39:25,390 --> 00:39:26,910
Will she protect this good friend of hers

799
00:39:26,910 --> 00:39:29,380
whole-heartedly?

800
00:39:29,950 --> 00:39:31,230
What do you think will happen to her?

801
00:39:31,790 --> 00:39:33,150
She'll then

802
00:39:34,350 --> 00:39:36,670
be against Director Yang.

803
00:39:38,590 --> 00:39:40,430
I'm not sure if this counts

804
00:39:40,430 --> 00:39:42,230
as a flaw in her work.

805
00:40:02,940 --> 00:40:04,350
[Who's that? Didn't you see me?]

806
00:40:04,670 --> 00:40:05,990
[I'm sorry, Brother Xiao Chen.]

807
00:40:05,990 --> 00:40:07,310
[I did not do it on purpose.]

808
00:40:07,790 --> 00:40:09,030
[It's you, Xiao Niao.]

809
00:40:09,190 --> 00:40:10,190
-[I'll help you pick them up.]
-[It's fine.]

810
00:40:10,190 --> 00:40:10,910
[Let me do it.]

811
00:40:10,910 --> 00:40:13,070
[Do you want to go to get that checked
at the hospital?]

812
00:40:13,070 --> 00:40:14,550
[It's nothing. I'm not that weak.]

813
00:40:14,550 --> 00:40:16,910
[Let's go. I'll send you
to the editorial department.]

814
00:40:16,910 --> 00:40:18,950
[Thank you, Brother Xiao Chen.
You're such a nice person.]

815
00:40:18,950 --> 00:40:20,190
[This is just what I should do.]

816
00:40:21,420 --> 00:40:22,860
[Xiao Niao just stood there]

817
00:40:22,860 --> 00:40:24,870
[and barely moved.]

818
00:40:24,870 --> 00:40:26,750
[And she found a free worker.]

819
00:40:29,230 --> 00:40:30,990
[I've got it, Chu Li.
You try acting as a spoilt kid too.]

820
00:40:31,470 --> 00:40:32,190
[What?]

821
00:40:32,830 --> 00:40:34,420
[You act like a spoilt kid too!]

822
00:40:35,950 --> 00:40:36,830
[Are you suggesting that]

823
00:40:36,830 --> 00:40:39,190
[I should act like a spoilt kid
to Mr Zhou Chuan?]

824
00:40:40,390 --> 00:40:43,830
Acting like a spoilt kid...
Could it be that it's useful?

825
00:41:02,870 --> 00:41:07,510
My stomachache!

826
00:41:08,350 --> 00:41:12,700
Mr Zhou Chuan, are you at home?

827
00:41:12,910 --> 00:41:17,710
My stomachache!

828
00:41:21,150 --> 00:41:24,030
Mr Zhou Chuan!

829
00:41:24,030 --> 00:41:26,390
Mr Zhou Chuan, I can't stand it!

830
00:41:26,390 --> 00:41:32,300
My stomach really hurts, Mr Zhou Chuan!

831
00:41:36,550 --> 00:41:39,660
Mr Zhou Chuan, please save me!

832
00:41:39,660 --> 00:41:41,270
My stomach really hurts!

833
00:41:41,270 --> 00:41:44,180
Mr Zhou Chuan, I can't stand it!

834
00:41:45,830 --> 00:41:47,950
Mr Zhou Chuan!

835
00:41:53,350 --> 00:41:54,830
Where did he go?

836
00:41:55,110 --> 00:41:56,190
Where did who go?

837
00:42:02,510 --> 00:42:05,390
Mr Zhou! So, you were at home!

838
00:42:05,390 --> 00:42:07,990
It's okay.
Please continue your performance.

839
00:42:10,790 --> 00:42:13,110
Mr Zhou Chuan, I know that

840
00:42:13,110 --> 00:42:15,910
you're a stream of clarity
in the literary world,

841
00:42:15,910 --> 00:42:18,110
and the solitary wolf on the plains.

842
00:42:19,190 --> 00:42:20,990
But it is really very hard

843
00:42:20,990 --> 00:42:23,750
to get shortlisted in Huazhi Award!

844
00:42:23,750 --> 00:42:25,790
Think about it. If you win,

845
00:42:25,790 --> 00:42:27,150
then you'll earn something!

846
00:42:27,150 --> 00:42:29,180
Even if you don't win anything,
you don't lose anything too.

847
00:42:29,740 --> 00:42:30,910
From now onwards,

848
00:42:30,910 --> 00:42:32,150
if you say another word

849
00:42:32,150 --> 00:42:34,140
about this matter,

850
00:42:34,140 --> 00:42:35,310
I will start charging you rent.

851
00:42:35,310 --> 00:42:36,780
It starts from 1,000 yuan with no limit.

852
00:42:37,830 --> 00:42:39,470
Mr Zhou Chuan,

853
00:42:39,470 --> 00:42:41,310
participating in the Huazhi Award

854
00:42:41,310 --> 00:42:43,790
is really beneficial for you.

855
00:42:43,790 --> 00:42:46,350
Mr Xia is different

856
00:42:46,350 --> 00:42:47,710
from me who treat authors

857
00:42:47,710 --> 00:42:49,470
as weapons to obtain fame.

858
00:42:49,470 --> 00:42:51,990
He really does mean well for you.

859
00:42:54,750 --> 00:42:55,790
The words that you just said

860
00:42:55,790 --> 00:42:56,590
inclusive of the punctuation marks

861
00:42:56,590 --> 00:42:57,790
cost you the rent of 10,800 yuan

862
00:42:57,790 --> 00:42:58,830
every month.

863
00:43:02,860 --> 00:43:05,380
I can't even afford 1,800 yuan.

864
00:43:05,380 --> 00:43:08,950
Where will I find
the money to pay 10,800 yuan?

865
00:43:11,830 --> 00:43:15,870
Mr Zhou Chuan!

866
00:43:15,870 --> 00:43:18,390
Won't you consider it even a little?
